{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VBLsryvRxb2UxZXaBhoZn6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01T6LvuvJXZTAG4vi4TCEVYZ","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/sksizer2/Developer/DarkFactory/.worktrees/PRD-222-general-purpose-tool/prds/PRD-222.8-dogfood-move-state.md","content":"---\nid: \"PRD-222.8\"\ntitle: \"Dogfood: move darkfactory's own state to .darkfactory/\"\nkind: task\nstatus: ready\npriority: high\neffort: m\ncapability: moderate\nparent: \"[[PRD-222-general-purpose-tool]]\"\ndepends_on:\n  - \"[[PRD-222.1-config-directory-discovery]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-222.2-prd-init-subcommand]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-222.3-bundle-builtin-workflows]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-222.5-cascade-resolver-workflows]]\"\n  - \"[[PRD-222.6-cascade-resolver-config]]\"\nblocks: []\nimpacts:\n  - .darkfactory/prds/\n  - .darkfactory/config.toml\n  - .gitignore\n  - prds/\nworkflow: null\ntarget_version: null\ncreated: 2026-04-08\nupdated: 2026-04-08\ntags:\n  - harness\n  - config\n---\n\n# Dogfood: move darkfactory's own state to .darkfactory/\n\n## Summary\n\nApply the `.darkfactory/` convention to darkfactory's own repository. Run `prd init` against the repo root, move all existing PRDs from `prds/` to `.darkfactory/prds/`, remove the old top-level `prds/` directory, and verify that every harness flow works against darkfactory's own clone using the same code path as any other project. No dev-mode fallback, no special-case detection.\n\n## Requirements\n\n1. Run `prd init` in darkfactory's own repo to create the `.darkfactory/` structure.\n2. Move all files from `prds/` to `.darkfactory/prds/` preserving filenames and content.\n3. Delete the old top-level `prds/` directory after the move.\n4. Update `.gitignore` to include `.darkfactory/worktrees/` and `.darkfactory/transcripts/` (should be handled by `prd init`).\n5. Update any code, scripts, CI config, or documentation that references the old `prds/` path to use `.darkfactory/prds/`.\n6. Verify all harness flows work: `prd status`, `prd validate`, `prd tree`, `prd list-workflows`, `prd run`, workflow execution.\n7. Confirm there is no dev-mode fallback anywhere — grep the codebase for any `prds/` hardcoded paths or `pyproject.toml` sniffing and remove them.\n8. The CLAUDE.md or any harness configuration referencing `prds/` must be updated.\n\n## Technical Approach\n\n### Step 1: Initialize\n\n```bash\nprd init  # creates .darkfactory/ at repo root\n```\n\n### Step 2: Move PRDs\n\n```bash\nmv prds/*.md .darkfactory/prds/\nrmdir prds  # or rm -r if it has subdirectories\n```\n\n### Step 3: Update references\n\nSearch for hardcoded `prds/` references:\n- `src/darkfactory/cli.py` — `_default_prd_dir` should already be gone (PRD-222.1), but verify.\n- `CLAUDE.md` — update any instructions referencing `prds/`.\n- `.github/workflows/` — update CI if it references `prds/`.\n- `tests/` — update test fixtures that assume `prds/` at repo root.\n- `README.md` — should already be updated by PRD-222.7.\n\n### Step 4: Verify\n\nRun the full suite:\n```bash\nprd validate\nprd status\nprd tree\nprd list-workflows\n```\n\nAll should work against `.darkfactory/prds/` without any special-case logic.\n\n### Step 5: Grep for remnants\n\n```bash\ngrep -r '\"prds/\"' src/ tests/\ngrep -r \"'prds/'\" src/ tests/\ngrep -r 'prds/' .github/ CLAUDE.md\n```\n\nRemove or update any remaining references.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] AC-1: `.darkfactory/` directory exists at the repo root with the standard layout.\n- [ ] AC-2: All existing PRD files are under `.darkfactory/prds/`.\n- [ ] AC-3: The old top-level `prds/` directory no longer exists.\n- [ ] AC-4: `prd validate` passes against `.darkfactory/prds/`.\n- [ ] AC-5: `prd status`, `prd tree`, and `prd list-workflows` work correctly.\n- [ ] AC-6: No hardcoded `prds/` paths remain in `src/` or `tests/`.\n- [ ] AC-7: No dev-mode fallback or pyproject.toml sniffing anywhere in the codebase.\n- [ ] AC-8: `.gitignore` excludes `.darkfactory/worktrees/` and `.darkfactory/transcripts/`.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8140,"cache_read_input_tokens":31410,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":8140},"output_tokens":72,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"939fc375-8ed1-4dc0-8515-8b3ee2d79451","uuid":"b4fc010a-5c66-4da4-9c05-71241d15a286"}
